NOTES.Electric motor, output:
96 kW/131 hp, maximum torque: 250 Nm (184 lb-ft)

Internal combustion engine: 170 kW/231 hp, maximum torque: 320 Nm (236 lb-ft)

Total system output: 266 kW/362 hp (max. torque: 570 Nm / 420 lb-ft)

Driving Experience Control switch and eDrive button allow driver to choose from five driving modes:
- range of up to 35 kilometres (22 miles) on electric power alone and a top speed of 120 km/h (75 mph);
- COMFORT mode offers optimum balance between dynamics and efficiency; combined range in everyday conditions: over 500 kilometres (310 miles);
- SPORT mode with ultra-intense boost function provided by the electric motor;
- ECO PRO mode can be used in both all-electric mode and hybrid mode.
